data.description: PRICE REDUCED ****Stunning property with a wonderful location just a few minutes away from the freeway I-10 with beautiful mountain views. This house features 3 -Bedrooms 2- Bathrooms. As you enter you will find the comfy living room with the cozy fireplace to enjoy the cold nights. New lovely blinds and new hard wood flooring almost throughout the house. Upgraded lighting and neutral paint colors to use your imagination to decorate the house using your favorite style. Spacious dining room with the back yard view open to the kitchen area. The kitchen has been updated with new stove and painted cabinets. Inside private laundry room with access to the main hallway. Master bedroom recently painted, new hard wood flooring and updated master bathroom. Bedrooms with great size to accommodate two beds in each bedroom. The main bathroom had been remodeled entirely. Huge two car garage and parking lot to accommodate your vehicles. Back yard with plenty space to spend time with your family and friends. Close to restaurants, shopping centers and medical offices. Don't miss out this opportunity to buy this great property it will go super fast. A must see!
